snippet.textDisplay:
I am so sorry to hear about you and your loved one breaking up. I know exactly how you are feeling. Me and my girlfriend of 4 and a half years just broke up and I have lost everything from the car I was driving, a cat named Paisley, to a little girl I called my step daughter (even though she wasn't legally mine).
Others are going through what you are right now, at this exact time, and we are all feeling lost. I think one of the best things to do is to reach out to others for support, wether it's new friends or old ones.
It sounds crazy, but I have a feeling like 2020 is going to be a little Rocky at first, but then it's going to pick up momentum later and will be one of the most significant years of our lives in terms of growth and experiences. Maybe we will look back at this and see that this isn't the time in our lives that we wanted, but rather the time that we needed.
Wishing you the best in everything!!!
